    <a title="Sandy Thomson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1139338-sandy-thomson"><img alt="Sandy Thomson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1213236469p2/1139338.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
