<span id="freeTextContainer17390341454480294633">Exceptional! I’m dumbfounded at the relief I feel having finished this book today. I have been transfixed each time I picked it up. This is no simple story and there are no real answers, but the journey is unforgettable. If you think you know people, dear reader, abandon all of your preconceived notions before starting on this story. </span>

          </span>
