<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/54815902-in-this-place-together"><img alt="In This Place Together: A Palestinian&#39;s Journey to Collective Liberation" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1601939558l/54815902._SX98_.jpg" />
